Beginner/First Pass:

Book:
Modern Cosmology by Scott Dodelson and Fabian Walter
https://www.amazon.in/Modern-Cosmology-Scott-Dodelson/dp/0128159480


Lecture Notes:
Daniel Baumann: https://cmb.wintherscoming.no/pdfs/baumann.pdf
SS Komissarov: https://www1.maths.leeds.ac.uk/~serguei/teaching/cosmology.pdf (A University level approach to cosmology)
Chris Hirata: hirata10.github.io/ph8803/ (Intro level cosmology)

Advanced/Second Pass:

Book:
Cosmology by Steven Weinberg

Lecture Notes:
